{
  "_comment": "NON-NORMATIVE benchmark fixture for RFC-003 follow-up. Structural expectations for the optional edge-case scenarios under fixtures/edge_cases/. These are NOT consumed by the v1 dry-run runner; they are scored by tests/test_edge_cases.py and by a future runner iteration. No schema, no normative status.",
  "fixture_version": "1",
